-- Rubalcaba to Run for Top Job in Spain Socialist Party, Efe Says
-- B y   A n g e l i n e   B e n o i t
-- 2011-12-28T10:20:50Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-28/rubalcaba-to-run-for-top-job-in-spain-socialist-party-efe-says.html
Alfredo Perez Rubalcaba, the losing
socialist candidate in  Spain ’s Nov. 20 elections, will announce
tomorrow that he’s running for the post of party general
secretary; former defense minister Carme Chacon is another
potential candidate, the newswire Efe reported, citing
unidentified party sources.  To contact the reporter on this story:
